      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a student.\n1. The applicant should be from a Denotified, Nomadic, and Semi-Nomadic Community.\n1. The applicant should be studying in Class 6th to 10th.\n\n_*The applicant should be eligible for the scholarship even if they have failed one year._\n_*The applicant should not need to reapply for renewal if they continue in the same category of classes (e.g., 6th to 8th or 9th to 10th)._\n",
